sequenceDiagram
    participant A as 发送者前端
    participant WS as ChatWebSocket
    participant MQ as RabbitMQ
    participant C as ChatMessageConsumer
    participant MG as MongoDB
    participant MySQL as MySQL message表
    participant Redis as Redis
    participant SSE as SseEmitterManager

    A->>A: 乐观更新：本地显示消息(status=sending)
    A->>WS: wsSend({type:"text", content})
    WS->>MQ: chatMessageProducer.sendChatMessage()
    MQ->>C: 消费消息
    C->>C: 检查接收者在线 → false
    C->>MG: 保存消息(status=sent，直接标记送达)
    C->>WS: broadcastToConversation()
    WS->>A: {type:"message", data} (status=sent，不转圈)
    C->>MySQL: 写通知消息(type=chat)
    C->>Redis: 未读数+1
    C->>SSE: sendToUser(receiverId, "message", notification)
    Note over SSE: 接收者离线，推送静默丢弃
